@startuml Dictionary Form TEA Logic Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

title Dictionary Form - Pure TEA Logic

actor User
participant "UI" as UI
participant Reducer
participant "Data Handler" as DH
participant "Nav Handler" as NH
participant "Flow Handler" as FH

== Структура состояния ==
note over Reducer
**DictionaryFormScreenState:**
|- editingDictionaryId: Long? = null
|}  |-- ID словаря для редактирования (null = создание)
|- name: String = ""
|}  |-- Текст в поле названия словаря
|- flagFilter: String = ""
|}  |-- Текст в поле фильтрации флагов
|- flags: List<CountryFlagItem> = emptyList()
|}  |-- Отфильтрованные флаги для отображения в grid
|- selectedFlag: CountryFlagItem? = null
|}  |-- Выбранный флаг (null = placeholder)
|- saveButtonEnabled: Boolean = false
|}  |-- Активность кнопки, = name.isNotBlank()

**Ключевые инварианты:**
- saveButtonEnabled = name.isNotBlank()
- editingDictionaryId неизменен после инициализации
- flags обновляется реактивно через FlowHandler
- allFlags хранится в UseCase, не в State
end note

== Инициализация (создание) ==
note over UI : Initial State:\n- editingDictionaryId = null\n- name = ""\n- saveButtonEnabled = false
note over FH : subscribe:\nUseCase.flagsFlow()\n→ FlagsUpdated(allFlags)

FH -> Reducer : Msg.FlagsUpdated(allFlags)
note right : State change:\nflags = allFlags

== Инициализация (редактирование) — параллельно ==
note over UI : Initial State:\n- editingDictionaryId = id\ninitEffects: LoadDictionary(id)
note over FH : subscribe:\nUseCase.flagsFlow()\n→ FlagsUpdated(allFlags)

FH -> Reducer : Msg.FlagsUpdated(allFlags)
note right : State change:\nflags = allFlags

Reducer -> DH : LoadDictionary(id)
note over DH : useCase.getDictionary(id)\nuseCase.findFlag(numericCode)
DH -> Reducer : Msg.DictionaryLoaded(name, flag)
note right : State change:\nname = dictName\nselectedFlag = flag\nsaveButtonEnabled = true

== Ввод названия ==
User -> UI : Type "English"
UI -> Reducer : Msg.NameChanged("English")

Reducer -> UI : newState
note right : State change:\nname = "English"\nsaveButtonEnabled = true

== Фильтрация флагов ==
User -> UI : Type "ger" in filter
UI -> Reducer : Msg.FlagFilterChanged("ger")

Reducer -> UI : newState
note right : State change:\nflagFilter = "ger"

Reducer -> FH : Effect.FilterFlags("ger")
note over FH : useCase.updateFilter("ger")\n→ debounce 300ms\n→ фильтрация в UseCase
FH -> Reducer : Msg.FlagsUpdated(filtered)
note right : State change:\nflags = filtered

== Выбор флага ==
User -> UI : Tap on flag (not selected)
UI -> Reducer : Msg.SelectFlag(item)

Reducer -> UI : newState
note right : State change:\nselectedFlag = item

== Снятие выбора флага ==
User -> UI : Tap on already selected flag
UI -> Reducer : Msg.SelectFlag(item) [item == selectedFlag]

Reducer -> UI : newState
note right : State change:\nselectedFlag = null

== Сохранение (создание) ==
User -> UI : Click "Создать"
UI -> Reducer : Msg.Save

Reducer -> DH : SaveDictionary(name, numericCode)
note right : numericCode = selectedFlag?.numericCode
DH -> DH : addDictionary + setCurrentDictionary
DH -> Reducer : Msg.DictionarySaved

Reducer -> NH : Effect.Close
note over NH : onClose()
NH -> Reducer : Msg.Empty

== Сохранение (редактирование) ==
User -> UI : Click "Сохранить"
UI -> Reducer : Msg.Save

Reducer -> DH : UpdateDictionary(id, name, numericCode)
DH -> DH : updateDictionary
DH -> Reducer : Msg.DictionarySaved

Reducer -> NH : Effect.Close
note over NH : onClose()
NH -> Reducer : Msg.Empty

== Навигация назад ==
User -> UI : Back press
UI -> Reducer : Msg.Back

Reducer -> NH : Effect.Back
note over NH : onBackPress()
NH -> Reducer : Msg.Empty

== Обработка сообщений ==
note over Reducer
**Reducer Logic:**
- NameChanged(value): updateName(value) → no effects
- FlagFilterChanged(query): updateFlagFilter(query) → Effect.FilterFlags(query)
- SelectFlag(item): toggle — if selected → deselect, else select → no effects
- Save: if editingId==null → SaveDictionary, else UpdateDictionary
- FlagsUpdated(list): updateFlags(list) → no effects
- DictionaryLoaded(name, flag): prefillForEdit(name, flag) → no effects
- DictionarySaved: no state → Effect.Close
- Back: no state → Effect.Back
- Empty: no-op
end note

== Effect Handlers ==
note over DH
**Data Handler:**
- LoadDictionary(id): load by id → DictionaryLoaded
- SaveDictionary(name, code): add + setCurrent → DictionarySaved
- UpdateDictionary(id, name, code): update → DictionarySaved
end note

note over NH
**Navigation Handler:**
- Close: onClose() → Msg.Empty
- Back: onBackPress() → Msg.Empty
end note

note over FH
**Flow Handler:**
- subscribe: useCase.flagsFlow() → Msg.FlagsUpdated(list)
- runEffect: FilterFlags(query) → useCase.updateFilter(query)
- Debounce 300ms в UseCase
- При старте эмитит все флаги (query пуст)
end note
@enduml
